snippet.title: 2017 Official Mini World/Block Art Trailer
snippet.description:
2017 Official Mini World/Block Art Trailer
Mini World is an FTP 3D  sandbox MMO  block-based adventure game set in a bizarre world where gathers a variety of unique cute monsters, blocks, materials, and mines to craft and explore.
Aims to be the best sandbox platform game.

Download: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.playmini.miniworld
